@baseUrl = http://localhost:8082
@token = replace-with-login-access-token

### 1. 查询全部库存流水
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stock-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 查询指定商品库存流水
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stock-logs?product_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 查询库存流水 - 非法 product_id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stock-logs?product_id=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 查询库存流水 - 非数字 product_id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stock-logs?product_id=abc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
